&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Security minded with the utmost regard for confidentiality and discretion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative and helpful by nature.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong sense of ownership in one’s work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communic

